<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 14:06:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>普京指责美国政策失败，俄罗斯表示正在与以色列和巴勒斯坦进行对话</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/russia-says-its-talking-to-both-israel-and-palestinians-as-putin-blames-failure-of-us-policy/articleshow/104319598.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104319598.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯总统普京周二表示，以色列和巴勒斯坦之间的暴力爆发表明美国中东政策的失败，克里姆林宫表示正在与交战双方保持联系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 13:21:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/russia-says-its-talking-to-both-israel-and-palestinians-as-putin-blames-failure-of-us-policy/articleshow/104319598.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列冲突爆发后英国反犹太主义事件激增</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-antisemitic-incidents-soar-after-start-of-conflict-in-israel/articleshow/104318598.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104318598.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据犹太慈善机构社区安全信托基金 (CST) 称，英国反犹太主义事件的报道与去年同期相比增加了两倍。尽管没有提供确切的数字，但 CST 预计未来几天将会报告更多事件。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 12:42:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-antisemitic-incidents-soar-after-start-of-conflict-in-israel/articleshow/104318598.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国人权事务高级专员谴责以色列“围困”加沙、武装分子劫持人质</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/un-rights-chief-condemns-israeli-siege-of-gaza-militants-taking-of-hostages/articleshow/104317662.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104317662.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国人权事务高级专员表示，以色列空袭的目标是加沙地带的住宅楼和学校。联合国还谴责巴勒斯坦武装组织的大规模杀戮和绑架人质。以色列军方已征召了30万名预备役军人，并对加沙实施全面封锁，可能是为了准备地面进攻。空袭袭击了联合国救援机构驻地，造成平民伤亡。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 12:13:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/un-rights-chief-condemns-israeli-siege-of-gaza-militants-taking-of-hostages/articleshow/104317662.cms</guid></item><item><title>德国检察官对哈马斯展开谋杀和绑架调查</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/german-prosecutor-opens-murder-and-kidnapping-probe-into-hamas/articleshow/104314958.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104314958.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;德国对哈马斯成员涉嫌谋杀、过失杀人和劫持人质展开调查。这项调查是在德国公民在哈马斯袭击以色列期间被绑架之后进行的。德国总理肖尔茨表示，他们正在与以色列合作，确保被绑架公民的自由和安全。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 11:09:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/german-prosecutor-opens-murder-and-kidnapping-probe-into-hamas/articleshow/104314958.cms</guid></item><item><title>法院驳回美国记者格什科维奇针对俄罗斯拘留的申诉</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/court-rejects-complaint-by-us-reporter-gershkovich-against-detention-in-russia/articleshow/104314422.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104314422.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯一家法院驳回了美国记者埃文·格什科维奇针对延长审前拘留的申诉。格什科维奇是《华尔街日报》的记者，今年三月因间谍罪被捕，但他否认了这一指控。法院的裁决意味着格什科维奇将至少被拘留到 11 月 30 日。审判日期尚未确定。格什科维奇是冷战以来首位因间谍罪在俄罗斯被拘留的美国记者。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 10:54:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/court-rejects-complaint-by-us-reporter-gershkovich-against-detention-in-russia/articleshow/104314422.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国在细菌恐慌后将寻求庇护者送回驳船</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/britain-to-return-asylum-seekers-to-barge-after-bacteria-scare/articleshow/104312218.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104312218.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国将再次将寻求庇护者安置在其南部海岸的一艘驳船上，两个月前，他们因水污染而被转移。政府希望削减安置移民的成本，但批评者称驳船不人道。这艘船是英国阻止人们从法国乘小船穿越英吉利海峡非法移民战略的一部分。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 09:51:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/britain-to-return-asylum-seekers-to-barge-after-bacteria-scare/articleshow/104312218.cms</guid></item><item><title>西方公司为土耳其无人机提供关键部件</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/western-firms-have-supplied-critical-components-for-turkish-drones/articleshow/104313715.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104313715.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 10:42:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/western-firms-have-supplied-critical-components-for-turkish-drones/articleshow/104313715.cms</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜指责以色列造成加沙流血事件</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinese-coast-guard-claims-to-have-chased-away-philippine-navy-ship-from-contested-south-china-sea-shoal/articleshow/104312336.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104312336.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国海警声称，他们将一艘菲律宾海军舰艇驱逐出南海有争议的浅滩。据称，这艘菲律宾船只驶入黄岩岛附近海域，该海域位于菲律宾专属经济区内。两国之间的紧张局势因南海丰富的渔区而不断升级。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 09:56:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinese-coast-guard-claims-to-have-chased-away-philippine-navy-ship-from-contested-south-china-sea-shoal/articleshow/104312336.cms</guid></item><item><title>中东危机考验中国外交努力的极限</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/middle-east-crisis-tests-limits-of-chinas-diplomatic-push/articleshow/104311303.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104311303.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;当中国今年出人意料地宣布一项恢复沙特阿拉伯和伊朗关系的协议时，这表明北京希望成为中东的外交重量级人物。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 09:28:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/middle-east-crisis-tests-limits-of-chinas-diplomatic-push/articleshow/104311303.cms</guid></item><item><title>在猛烈轰炸下，加沙的巴勒斯坦人从一个地方搬到另一个地方，却发现没有地方是安全的</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/under-heavy-bombing-palestinians-in-gaza-move-from-place-to-place-only-to-discover-nowhere-is-safe/articleshow/104310163.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104310163.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于以色列战机继续轰炸加沙地带，超过 18 万巴勒斯坦人正在加沙地带的联合国设施中寻求庇护。针对哈马斯武装分子袭击的空袭造成了广泛的破坏和人员伤亡。许多巴勒斯坦人，包括有孩子的家庭，被困在冲突地区，无处可去。以色列和埃及长达16年的封锁使局势更加恶化。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 08:51:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/under-heavy-bombing-palestinians-in-gaza-move-from-place-to-place-only-to-discover-nowhere-is-safe/articleshow/104310163.cms</guid></item><item><title>塞浦路斯表示准备在需要时协助以色列撤离</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/cyprus-says-ready-to-assist-israel-evacuations-if-needed/articleshow/104309759.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104309759.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在周末哈马斯武装分子对以色列发动意外袭击后，塞浦路斯外交部周二表示，塞浦路斯已准备好帮助撤离可能想要离开以色列的第三国国民。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 08:41:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/cyprus-says-ready-to-assist-israel-evacuations-if-needed/articleshow/104309759.cms</guid></item><item><title>法国臭虫也入侵英国了吗？伦敦市长萨迪克·汗发出警告引发恐慌</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/have-the-french-bedbugs-invaded-uk-too-panic-as-london-mayor-sadiq-khan-issues-warning/articleshow/104305756.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104305756.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在巴黎大面积爆发臭虫之后，伦敦市长萨迪克·汗对臭虫可能侵扰该市公共交通的可能性表示严重担忧。来自巴黎的视频显示臭虫在公共汽车和火车的座位上爬行，这引起了人们的警惕。汗一直在与巴黎官员联系，以更好地了解情况。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 06:42:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/have-the-french-bedbugs-invaded-uk-too-panic-as-london-mayor-sadiq-khan-issues-warning/articleshow/104305756.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯大规模袭击引发激烈战斗后，航空公司暂停进出以色列的航班</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/airlines-halt-flights-in-and-out-of-israel-after-a-massive-attack-by-hamas-ignites-heavy-fighting/articleshow/104305242.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104305242.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列因哈马斯袭击而宣战后，主要航空公司已暂停往返以色列的航班。以色列对加沙发动空袭，巴勒斯坦武装分子则对耶路撒冷和特拉维夫发动火箭袭击。美国航空、联合航空、达美航空、法国航空、汉莎航空、国泰航空、维珍航空、维兹航空、易捷航空、英国航空和荷兰皇家航空等航空公司均已暂停或取消飞往特拉维夫的航班。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 06:20:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/airlines-halt-flights-in-and-out-of-israel-after-a-massive-attack-by-hamas-ignites-heavy-fighting/articleshow/104305242.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国、英国、德国、意大利、法国向以色列提供支持</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/us-uk-germany-italy-france-extend-support-to-israel/articleshow/104304935.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104304935.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国、德国、法国、意大利发表联合声明，谴责哈马斯恐怖行径，表示支持以色列。他们强调巴勒斯坦人民的合法愿望，呼吁为以色列人和巴勒斯坦人争取正义和自由。领导人表示，哈马斯并不代表这些愿望，只会带来恐怖和流血。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 06:10:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/us-uk-germany-italy-france-extend-support-to-israel/articleshow/104304935.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列边境安全期间发现1500具哈马斯武装分子尸体</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/1500-bodies-of-hamas-militants-found-in-israel-as-it-claims-full-control-over-border/articleshow/104304315.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104304315.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列军方声称已经控制了边境，并报告称在以色列境内发现了1500具哈马斯武装分子的尸体。军方袭击了加沙数百个哈马斯目标，并敦促居民撤离。日本政府对冲突地区日本公民的安全以及对能源供应的影响表示担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 05:57:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/1500-bodies-of-hamas-militants-found-in-israel-as-it-claims-full-control-over-border/articleshow/104304315.cms</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜指责以色列造成加沙流血事件</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/north-korea-blames-israel-for-causing-bloodshed-in-gaza/articleshow/104302967.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104302967.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;朝鲜官方媒体指责以色列在加沙造成流血事件，并将以色列与哈马斯之间的军事冲突归咎于他们。这是朝鲜首次对冲突发表评论。该媒体援引外国消息人士的话称，此次冲突是以色列对巴勒斯坦人民持续犯罪行为造成的。加沙的暴力事件引发国际社会呼吁停止战斗并保护平民。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 05:25:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/north-korea-blames-israel-for-causing-bloodshed-in-gaza/articleshow/104302967.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯袭击：以色列电视名人的妹妹以“处决方式”被杀</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-hamas-attack-maayan-adam-mapal-adam-nova-trance-music-festival/articleshow/104302234.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104302234.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 27 岁的以色列妇女马帕尔·亚当 (Mapal Adam) 被哈马斯枪手“处决”。马帕尔躲在一辆卡车下，希望通过装死来生存。但她最终还是被袭击者发现了。她的妹妹、电视主持人 Maayan Adam 在 Instagram 上分享了这一令人心碎的消息，描述了马帕尔的最后时刻，并表达了家人的巨大悲痛。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 05:09:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-hamas-attack-maayan-adam-mapal-adam-nova-trance-music-festival/articleshow/104302234.cms</guid></item><item><title>警察称汽车冲撞中国驻旧金山领事馆，警察开枪打死司机</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/car-rams-into-chinese-consulate-in-san-francisco-and-police-fatally-shoot-driver-officers-say/articleshow/104301717.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104301717.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 04:42:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/car-rams-into-chinese-consulate-in-san-francisco-and-police-fatally-shoot-driver-officers-say/articleshow/104301717.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列大使馆、Chabad House 加强安全保卫</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/security-tightened-out-israel-embassy-chabad-house/articleshow/104301941.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104301941.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 04:51:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/security-tightened-out-israel-embassy-chabad-house/articleshow/104301941.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯-以色列冲突：习近平的反应暴露了中国作为和平缔造者的局限性</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/hamas-attack-on-israel-xi-jinpings-reaction-exposes-chinas-limits-as-peacemaker/articleshow/104301392.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104301392.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国领导人习近平试图在乌克兰和沙特阿拉伯-伊朗等冲突中扮演全球和平缔造者的角色，但在以色列与哈马斯冲突中遇到了绊脚石。中国关于冲突的最初声明避免点名侵略者，也没有立即提供援助。尽管中国将自己定位为全球参与者，但其对以色列与哈马斯冲突的反应有限，这引发了人们对其能否为棘手冲突提供持久解决方案的质疑。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 04:40:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/hamas-attack-on-israel-xi-jinpings-reaction-exposes-chinas-limits-as-peacemaker/articleshow/104301392.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>